nodes.text: Kashyyyk ale was a type of alcoholic beverage. Supplies of Kashyyyk ale were carried aboard the space yacht Imru Ootmian, to cater to the tastes of the Wookiee associates of the Hutt Zonnos Anjiliac Priare. In 19 ABY, a banquet was held in the penthouse of Zonnos' father Popara on the moon Nar Shaddaa, and Kashyyyk ale was served during the event.
